{"locales":{"en":{"3lusu7ek2d":{"lh_a168_title":"About Us","desc_html":"At <b>ShopSolar<\/b> (formerly Shop Solar Kits\u2122), we\u2019re cutting through the solar industry\u2019s overpriced nonsense to make energy independence simple, transparent and affordable. Since 2018, we\u2019ve shipped over 50,000 orders to cabins, homes, properties and businesses for customers across the U.S. We\u2019ve proven that you don\u2019t need a massive operations team, flashy vans, or overpriced consultation fees to harness the power of the sun. <br><br>\nWe started in Canada (yes, Canada) and quickly realized the real opportunity was south of the border. Fast forward 7+ years, and we\u2019re now one of the most trusted names in solar, helping people ditch inflated bills, power off-grid adventures, and stay prepared with reliable backup power.<br><br>\nAnd no, we don\u2019t ship your products from Canada. We have a completely separate US operation, so when you buy from us, you are buying from an <b>American based company.<\/b><!--lh-live-editor-->"},"4yxhtc0927d":{"lh_a168_title":"Trusted by 50,000+ & Counting","desc_html":"The internet can feel like the Wild West\u2014full of smoke, mirrors, and too-good-to-be-true promises. We get it\u2014trust doesn\u2019t come easy. But here\u2019s the thing: we\u2019re real, our systems work, and over 50,000 happy customers can vouch for us.<br><br>\nWe answer our phones, respond to emails, ship fast, and focus on what we do best: saving you money while powering your life. See a deal somewhere else that seems too good to be true? It probably is. If the website looks sketchy or they\u2019re skipping sales tax, it\u2019s not just shady\u2014it\u2019s illegal, and you\u2019ll end up footing the bill come tax season (someone has to).<br><br>\nHere\u2019s the good news: we\u2019ll match real deals from legitimate companies. So, shop smart and stay safe\u2014your trust deserves nothing less.<br><br><!--lh-live-editor-->"},"hiirl47vfup":{"lh_a168_title":"How We Beat the Big Guys","desc_html":"Here\u2019s the solar industry\u2019s dirty secret: you\u2019re not paying for panels; you\u2019re paying for their bloated overhead - Commissions, markups, vehicles, and hidden fees - That\u2019s their problem, not yours.<br><br>\nAt ShopSolar, we keep it lean. No pushy salespeople. No overpriced systems. Just high-quality solar kits at prices that make traditional installers sweat. And yes, batteries are included \u2013 because a solar system without storage is like a car without a gas tank.<br><br>\n\nWe also use modern eCommerce logistics and supply chain optimization techniques to cut costs wherever possible. Sometimes that means buying and stocking inventory; other times, it means drop-shipping directly to you (yes, we said drop-shipping). Whatever makes the most sense to save our customers money, we do it.<!--lh-live-editor-->"},"oguopnqy2cs":{"lh_a168_title":"Meet Our Founders","desc_html":"In 2018, Alex and Max launched ShopSolar to fix an industry stuck in the 90\u2019s. What started in Canada quickly grew into a U.S. powerhouse, with tens of thousands of systems delivered and thousands of customers who now call the shots on their energy.<br><br>\nWe\u2019re here to simplify solar, strip out the nonsense, and help you gain true energy independence \u2013 whether you\u2019re off-grid, prepping for outages, or just tired of writing big checks to your utility company.<!--lh-live-editor-->"},"pax1nc6jv1h":{"lh_iy69ny_name":"Alex Smith","lh_iy69ny_job":"Co-Founder","lh_iy66lp_name":"Max BM","lh_iy66lp_job":"Co-Founder"},"g4l139dzzhi":{"lh_a168_title":"Join The Solar Revolution","desc_html":"You\u2019re here for one reason: to take control of your energy. We\u2019re here to help you do that \u2013 simply, affordably, and transparently.\n<br>\n<br><!--lh-live-editor-->"},"zrazqz9y9d":{"lh_a168_title_html":"Hear From Our Founder &amp; CEO:"},"r77p9vbl3w":{"lh_a168_title":"Locations","desc_html":"<span>Houston, TX | Ogdensburg, NY | Las Vegas, NV<\/span><br><br>\n\nIf you're looking for affordable solar equipment for your home, RV, off-grid property or anywhere else, look no further! You can rest assured we'll go above and beyond for you. <br><br>\n\nPlease reach out if you have any questions at all as we would love the chance to earn your business. Give us a call at <a href=\"tel:877-808-0234\">877-2<\/a>42-2792 (Yes, we actually answer the phone during regular business hours.)<br><br><!--lh-live-editor-->"}}},"name":"About Us"}
